---
// Benefits of products — 6 cards
---

<section
  id="beneficios"
  class="min-h-[calc(100vh-56px)] py-12 flex flex-col justify-center bg-gradient-to-bl from-surface via-deep-navy to-surface text-on-surface px-5 md:px-16 border-b border-ice-cyan/10 relative overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none"
    style="background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, #00BCD4 0%, transparent 50%);"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-center mb-6 text-frost-white">
      Beneficios de nuestros productos
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <!-- Sin Quemadura de Freezer -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">block</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Sin Quemadura de Freezer</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            Al eliminar el aire, protegemos la superficie del alimento contra la deshidratación y escarcha.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ahorra Espacio -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">kitchen</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Ahorra Espacio</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            El empaque plano y sin aire permite un almacenamiento eficiente y ordenado en tu congelador.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vida Útil 3-5x Mayor -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">update</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Vida Útil 3-5x Mayor</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            Sin oxígeno, el deterioro enzimático se detiene casi por completo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Marinado Instantáneo -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">water_drop</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Marinado Instantáneo</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            La presión del vacío abre los poros de la carne, absorbiendo sabores profundamente antes de congelar.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Ultracongelado -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">ac_unit</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Ultracongelado</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            Congelamos en minutos a -40°C formando microcristales que mantienen la textura, nutrientes y sabor intactos como recién cocinado.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Sellado al Vacío -->
      <div class="glass-frost p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-5 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,188,212,0.15)] duration-300 border-ice-cyan/20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-warm-copper text-5xl shrink-0">lock</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-2 text-frost-white">Sellado al Vacío</h3>
          <p class="text-[16px] text-pale-blue/80 font-light leading-relaxed">
            Eliminamos el oxígeno para evitar oxidación, quemadura por frío y olores cruzados. Frescura atrapada hasta por 12 meses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>